  "title": "Accurate Textures",
  "description": "More details, with same shape and color from the Default Minecraft textures.",
  "body": "**This pack keeps the same native color and the same native shape from the Default Minecraft textures.**\n\n- This pack aims on blocks and items. *(around 95% complete)*\n- Optifine is not needed.\n- Compatible from MC 1.13 to actual version.\n\n## What is an Accurate Texture?\n\n- Original color only: no new colors in the image.\n- Same amount of color: Histogram Average channel #color is identical to original 16x16 texture.\n- Respect of Minecraft: iconic parts of the design will be preserved. (a line of 1 pixel wide in 16x16 is 2 pixel wide in 32x32)\n\n\n\n## License\nif you want to use/mix my textures in another pack, please contact me, i would like to know where my textures are used.\nNO COMMERCIAL !!! Anyway, Mojang/Microsoft probably owns 1/4 of each texture.\nI can allow the use for people not making money with.\nOf course any public player can use it, please let a link in your video description or any way of credit. ;)\n\n## Credits\nSome textures from [ZeRafal's Truthful x32 resource pack](https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/truthful/) (details in Credits.txt).",
